Package: ThreeTests
Title: Provides a linear model test, a t-test, and a chi-squared test
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Joshua",
           family = "Austin",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "joshua.austin@students.mq.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Gives functions to run a linear model test of 2 variables, a t-test for 2 samples, and a chi-squared test accross 2 catagories. Package also provides the ProjectData dataset with physical attributes for 1000 people.
